title: All California Wildfire Evacuation Orders Have Been Lifted
description: All evacuation orders have been lifted more than a month after a devastating wildfire that wiped out the Northern California town Paradise.
content: (PARADISE, Calif.) — All evacuation orders have been lifted in Paradise more than a month after a devastating wildfire that wiped out the Northern California town. The fire that broke out Nov. 8 killed at least 86 people and destroyed 14,000 homes in Paradise… [+536 chars]
